## Standaard commando's

```bash
# Build (voor Mac, naar simulator)
xcodebuild build -scheme [SCHEME] -destination 'platform=iOS Simulator,name=iPhone 16'

# Tests
xcodebuild test -scheme [SCHEME] -destination 'platform=iOS Simulator,name=iPhone 16'

# Lint + format
swiftlint
swiftformat .

# Project regenereren (indien Tuist)
tuist generate

# Project regenereren (indien XcodeGen)
xcodegen generate
```

