## Architectuur ‚Äî kort

**Pragmatisch protocol-oriented met Core + modulaire features.**

```
App/                  # @main, AppEnvironment, root navigation
Core/                 # protocols, models, use cases ‚Äî geen UI
Infrastructure/       # concrete implementaties van Core-protocols
Features/             # modulair, √©√©n folder per feature
DesignSystem/         # tokens + components
Resources/            # assets, localizables
Tests/
```

Volledige regels in `docs/architecture.md`.

